		{"id":"d677c9c679803700","type":"text","text":"# ***ComponentVersion***\n\n\t_id: ObjectId\n\tversion: string\n","x":5080,"y":7486,"width":620,"height":200},
		{"id":"760cede53ed19dfc","type":"text","text":"# ***Page***\n\n\t_id: ObjectId\n\tstableId: ObjectId (식별)\n\trevisionId: ObjectId\n\tspaceId: ObjectId\n\trootPageTreeId: ObjectId\n\tname: string\n\torder: number\n\tx: number\n\ty: number\n\tviewportWidth: number\n\tviewportHeight: number","x":5530,"y":5780,"width":540,"height":360},
		{"id":"67e4f6d080ed0315","type":"text","text":"# ***PageTree***\n\n\t_id: ObjectId\n\tstableId: ObjectId (식별)\n\trevisionId: ObjectId\n\tpageId: ObjectId\n\tcomponentId: ObjectId\n\tcomponentVariantId: ObjectId | null\n\tparentId: ObjectId | null\n\tchildrenIds: ObjectId[]\n\torder: number","x":5530,"y":6170,"width":540,"height":340},
		{"id":"094c3602ec8541c9","type":"text","text":"# ***User***\n\n\t_id: ObjectId;\n\tloginId: string;\n\tname: string;\n\tpasswordHash: string;\n","x":6760,"y":3580,"width":540,"height":240},
		{"id":"d2c7e9cf04362ee2","type":"text","text":"# ***ProjectRole***\n\n```\nenum ProjectRole {\n  Owner,\n  Editor,\n  Viewer\n}\n```","x":8380,"y":8680,"width":360,"height":240},
		{"id":"978e89864db2b590","type":"text","text":"# ***UserSession***\n\n\t_id: ObjectId;\n\tuserId: ObjectId;\n\trefreshTokenHash: string;\n\texpiredTime: Date;\n\trevokedTime: Date | null;\n\tcreatedTime: Date;\n","x":6760,"y":4000,"width":540,"height":260},
		{"id":"d5d28ba710a8996c","type":"text","text":"# ***StyleRuleToDefaultValue***\n\n```\ntype StyleRuleToDefaultValue<R extends { primitive: Primitive }> = R extends {\n  units: readonly StyleValueUnit[];\n}\n  ? {\n      value: PrimitiveValue<R[\"primitive\"]>;\n      unit: R[\"units\"][number];\n    }\n  : R extends { formats: readonly StyleValueFormat[] }\n    ? {\n        value: PrimitiveValue<R[\"primitive\"]>;\n        format?: R[\"formats\"][number];\n      }\n    : {\n        value: PrimitiveValue<R[\"primitive\"]>;\n      };\n```\n","x":-2800,"y":1760,"width":580,"height":500},
		{"id":"789f87c87eb149f5","type":"text","text":"# ***RevisionStatus***\n\n```\nenum RevisionStatus {\n  Working,\n  Sealed\n}\n```","x":7960,"y":8680,"width":360,"height":240},
		{"id":"e6dc6b4ac72bc0e5","type":"text","text":"# ***ComponentVariant***\n\n\t_id: ObjectId\n\tcomponentId: ObjectId\n\tkey: string\n\tname: string\n\torder: number\n","x":5080,"y":8100,"width":620,"height":240},
		{"id":"d74f903d479d2bbb","type":"text","text":"# ***Component***\n\n\t_id: ObjectId\n\tcomponentVersionId: ObjectId\n\tname: string\n\ttagName: string\n","x":5080,"y":7760,"width":620,"height":240},
		{"id":"56fadaf9ee4ba03f","type":"text","text":"# ***Revision***\n\n\t_id: ObjectId\n\tprojectId: ObjectId\n\tparentRevisionId: ObjectId | null\n\tcomponentVersionId: ObjectId;\n\tcreatedBy: ObjectId\n\tdescription: string\n\tstatus: RevisionStatus\n","x":6290,"y":4500,"width":540,"height":290},
		{"id":"8f35e5b9923c2420","type":"text","text":"# ***Project***\n\n\t_id: ObjectId\n\tcurrentRevisionId: ObjectId\n\tcreatedBy: ObjectId\n\tname: string\n\tdescription: string\n","x":5530,"y":4500,"width":540,"height":290},
		{"id":"b5dab460c81155f8","type":"text","text":"# ***ProjectMember ***\n\n\t_id: ObjectId;\n\tprojectId: ObjectId;\n\tuserId: ObjectId;\n\trole: ProjectRole;\n","x":5530,"y":3593,"width":540,"height":215},
		{"id":"1308b7e0ef5a7404","type":"text","text":"# ***PageTreeStyleOverride***\n\t_id: ObjectId;\n\tpageTreeId: ObjectId;\n\tcomponentStyleId: ObjectId;\n\trevisionId: ObjectId\n\tstringValue: string | null;\n\tnumberValue: number | null;\n\tbooleanValue: boolean | null;\n\tunit: StyleValueUnit | null;\n\tformat: StyleValueFormat | null;\n\tdesignTokenValueId: ObjectId | null;","x":4810,"y":6720,"width":540,"height":350},
		{"id":"f20eb535ff24c2eb","type":"text","text":"# ***PrimitiveValue***\n\n```\ntype PrimitiveValue<P extends Primitive> = P extends Primitive.String\n  ? string\n  : P extends Primitive.Number\n    ? number\n    : P extends Primitive.Boolean\n      ? boolean\n      : never;\n```\n","x":-2800,"y":2320,"width":580,"height":300},
		{"id":"5b56ac51dc91719e","type":"text","text":"# ***Primitive***\n\n```\nenum Primitive {\n  String = \"string\",\n  Number = \"number\",\n  Boolean = \"boolean\",\n}\n```","x":-1440,"y":8680,"width":360,"height":240},
		{"id":"44872e9f150ed16d","type":"text","text":"# ***StyleValueFormat***\n\n```\nenum StyleValueFormat {\n  Hex = \"hex\",\n  Rgb = \"rgb\",\n  Rgba = \"rgba\",\n  Hsl = \"hsl\",\n  Hsla = \"hsla\",\n}\n```","x":-620,"y":8640,"width":360,"height":280},
		{"id":"ca9bbe1f79da89da","type":"text","text":"# ***StyleValueKind***\n\n```\nenum StyleValueKind {\n  Text = \"text\",\n  Color = \"color\",\n  Number = \"number\",\n  Length = \"length\",\n  Boolean = \"boolean\",\n}\n```","x":-1040,"y":8640,"width":360,"height":280},
		{"id":"d3d187606e62f2d5","type":"text","text":"# ***StyleValueUnit***\n\n```\nenum StyleValueUnit {\n  Px = \"px\",\n  Rem = \"rem\",\n  Percent = \"%\",\n}\n```","x":-200,"y":8680,"width":360,"height":240},
		{"id":"a07cc2bc5785a0cb","type":"text","text":"# ***STYLE_VALUE_KIND_RULES***\n\n```\nconst STYLE_VALUE_KIND_RULES = {\n  [StyleValueKind.Text]: {\n    primitive: Primitive.String,\n  },\n  [StyleValueKind.Color]: {\n    primitive: Primitive.String,\n    formats: [\n      StyleValueFormat.Hex,\n      StyleValueFormat.Rgb,\n      StyleValueFormat.Rgba,\n      StyleValueFormat.Hsl,\n      StyleValueFormat.Hsla,\n    ],\n  },\n  [StyleValueKind.Number]: {\n    primitive: Primitive.Number,\n  },\n  [StyleValueKind.Length]: {\n    primitive: Primitive.Number,\n    units: [StyleValueUnit.Px, StyleValueUnit.Rem, StyleValueUnit.Percent],\n  },\n  [StyleValueKind.Boolean]: {\n    primitive: Primitive.Boolean,\n  },\n};\n```","x":-2800,"y":8200,"width":1000,"height":720},
		{"id":"aea4cc65f2142cc6","type":"text","text":"# ***ComponentPropsDefinition***\n\n```\ninterface ComponentPropsDefinition {\n  style: ComponentStyleDefinition[];\n  attributes: [];\n  state: [];\n  slots: [];\n  accessibility: [];\n  data: [];\n  events: [];\n}\n```","x":-1640,"y":240,"width":760,"height":360},
		{"id":"c9b525b9cb125c59","type":"text","text":"# ***ComponentVariantDefinition***\n\n```\ninterface ComponentVariantDefinition {\n  key: string;\n  name: string;\n  order: number\n  props?: Partial<ComponentPropsDefinition>;\n}\n```","x":-600,"y":240,"width":760,"height":360},
		{"id":"09aeedb2cc299efc","type":"text","text":"# ***ComponentStyleDefaultValueMap ***\n\n```\ntype ComponentStyleDefaultValueMap = {\n  [K in keyof typeof STYLE_VALUE_KIND_RULES]: StyleRuleToDefaultValue<typeof STYLE_VALUE_KIND_RULES[K]>;\n};\n```\n","x":-2800,"y":1480,"width":580,"height":210},
		{"id":"3b7daeaddf98957a","type":"text","text":"# ***ComponentStyleDefaultValue ***\n\n```\ntype ComponentStyleDefaultValue<K extends StyleValueKind = StyleValueKind> =\n  ComponentStyleDefaultValueMap[K];\n```\n","x":-2800,"y":1210,"width":580,"height":210},
		{"id":"f7f6f28dbfb3a782","type":"text","text":"# ***ComponentStyleDefinition***\n\n```\ntype ComponentStyleDefinition<K extends StyleValueKind = StyleValueKind> = {\n  [P in K]: {\n    label: string;\n    cssProperty: keyof ElementCSSInlineStyle[\"style\"];\n    valueKind: P;\n    defaultValue?: ComponentStyleDefaultValue<P>;\n  };\n}[K];\n```\n","x":-2800,"y":820,"width":580,"height":320},
		{"id":"6ee489bb20fa0b94","type":"text","text":"# ***ComponentManifestModel***\n\n\tcomponentVersionId: string\n\trevisionId: string\n\tcomponentVersion: string\n\tcomponents: ComponentModel[]\n","x":3040,"y":340,"width":760,"height":220},
		{"id":"9e2ada353a085d22","type":"text","text":"# ***ComponentStyleModel***\n\n\tid: string\n\tcomponentVariantId: string | null\n\tprojectComponentStylePresetId: string | null\n\tlabel: string\n\tcssProperty: keyof ElementCSSInlineStyle[\"style\"]\n\tvalueKind: StyleValueKind\n\tstringValue: string | null;\n\tnumberValue: number | null;\n\tbooleanValue: boolean | null;\n\tunit: StyleValueUnit | null;\n\tformat: StyleValueFormat | null;\n\tdesignTokenId: string | null;\n\tdesignTokenValueId: string | null;","x":2400,"y":1860,"width":760,"height":440},
		{"id":"5c4eb6e0aa728ffe","type":"text","text":"# ***ComponentStyle***\n\n\t_id: ObjectId\n\tcomponentVariantId: ObjectId | null (null 이면 defaultProps)\n\tlabel: string\n\tcssProperty: keyof ElementCSSInlineStyle[\"style\"]\n\tvalueKind: StyleValueKind\n\tdefaultStringValue: string | null;\n\tdefaultNumberValue: number | null;\n\tdefaultBooleanValue: boolean | null;\n\tdefaultUnit: StyleValueUnit | null;\n\tdefaultFormat: StyleValueFormat | null\n","x":4440,"y":8426,"width":640,"height":354},
